0.04 (Released 2011-02-10)

    API Changes:
        - App::Dispatcher::app_dispatcher no longer exported by
          default.

    New Features:
        - None.

    Enhancements:
        - Collapsed App::Dispatcher::Command into App::Dispatcher.

    Bug Fixes:
        - Added missing dependency on Getopt::Long::Descriptive

